<Base title="Author" description="Meet Greg Simpson">
  <section class="section">
    <h1>Greg Simpson</h1>
    <p>
      Greg Simpson is an author and technologist. He enjoys writing compelling adventure and mystery novels which weave
      technology and science with real world intrigue. He is a traveler and adventurer. As a technologist, he runs a tech
      consulting firm that focuses on IT strategy for the healthcare industry.
    </p>
    <p>
      The Quotient Covenant is his first book and was released May 10, 2025. The story follows the adventures of Kara
      McClellan, the lead scientist in the series. The second book, Quantum Time, continues Kara's journey as she and her
      team confront a new quantum threat.
    </p>
    <p>
      Greg's inspiration for this series comes from his own background in advanced technology. He has a formal education
      in computer science, runs a consulting company, and has extensive experience in the technology sector. He strives to
      make the technology in the story as accurate as possible while providing an entertaining, fast-paced adventure for
      the reader.
    </p>
    <p>
      His love of travel has taken him around the world. Through these travels, he captures inspiration for real-world
      locations in the series, bringing the settings of the books to life in vivid detail. As of 2026, the series continues
      to expand with new research, new places, and the next stories in development.
    </p>
